Title: The q-Boson Realizations of the Quantum Group $U_{q}(sl(n+1,C))$
Authors: C. Burdik,L. Cerny and O. Navratil
Comments: 7pp
Report-no: PRA-HEP-92/13
Journal-ref: J.Phys. A26 (1993) L83-L88
\\
  We give explicit expression of recurrency formulae of canonical realization
for quantum enveloping algebras $U_{q}(sl(n+1,C))$. In these formulas the
generators of the algebra $U_{q}(sl(n+1,C))$ are expressed by means of
n-canonical q-boson pairs one auxiliary representation of the algebra
$U_{q}(gl(n,C))$.
